{
  "stem": "8834.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by us were a few kibbutzim, where people were working in the, in the mill where I was working.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave them jobs there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in other places from the kibbutzim, they came to work as women to clean the houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they have their own commune.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they waited to the-- after a period of time, they were going home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were waiting for a certificate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But sometimes they never got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the war broke out, and they went-- they perished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My one sister was married, during the war, 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was before the war, but in that year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had one child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very nice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't-- mostly it was outside the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the, the service was in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the canopy and everything was outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we went in for a, for a full meal at home or we-- on a bigger, big hall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just like here sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it wasn't so elaborate like here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But people lived very nicely and very, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even so, it wasn't so elaborate and so rich like here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't hear at home about so many divorces like I hear here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a good life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have-- my childhood was very, very simple.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So was my other sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't live so as people live here, the children do here, no, very simple and plain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we, we were very close to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that meant a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wanted to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so my father knew these people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he worked for them too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was the name of their company?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH] Lumber Mill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what did you do there?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
